tent/uploads/2023/12/Green-Day-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Green-Day-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Green-Day-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Green-Day-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/green-day">绿日乐队</a>的<a href="/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗</a>公开了他对米尔沃尔足球俱乐部和体验英国文化的热爱。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/10-albums-that-wouldnt-exist-without-green-days-dookie-768209">如果没有 Green Day 的《Dookie》，这 10 张专辑就不会存在</a></strong></li></ul><p>由阿姆斯特朗、贝斯手迈克·杜恩特和鼓手特雷·库尔组成的传奇流行朋克乐队在接受<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2023/dec/27/green-day-uk-tour-album-saviors" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>采访时谈到了他们即将发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-share-tracklist-for-new-album-saviors-3544330">《Saviors》</a> 。</p><p> Green Day 专辑的大部分内容是在伦敦的 RAK Studios 与长期制作人 Rob Cavallo 共同创作的。在被问及伦敦最喜欢的事情之后，阿姆斯特朗开始谈论他观看足球比赛的情况。</p><p> “我看了很多足球比赛：阿森纳、莱顿东方、富勒姆。我去The Den看米尔沃尔。那太精彩了。伙计，如果你真的想体验英国文化，那就应该这么做，”他说。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1WntIOtksz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bo